title: Sony LinkBuds S apparently borrow Pixel Buds vent to offer noise cancellation and open sound
content:
Sony’s unique LinkBuds doubled down on the idea of open sound in earbuds, but it seems their sibling may go for a more balanced approach. A leak claims to show off the “Sony LinkBuds S,” which have a vent similar to Google’s Pixel Buds.

more…

The post Sony LinkBuds S apparently borrow Pixel Buds vent to offer noise cancellation and open sound appeared first on 9to5Google.
description: A leak of the upcoming Sony LinkBuds S shows off the different design that uses a vent similar to what Google's Pixel Buds offer.
